You can pay securely using the link below:
${PAY_LINK}

If you have questions or believe this was sent in error, please reply to this email or contact us at ${FIRM_EMAIL}.

Thank you,
${FIRM_NAME}`
  },
  day7: {
    subject: `Second reminder: Invoice ${invoice.invoice_number} — 7 days past due`,
    body: `Hi ${invoice.client_name},

We wanted to follow up on invoice ${invoice.invoice_number} for $${Number(invoice.balance).toFixed(2)}, which remains unpaid 7 days past the due date of ${invoice.due_date}.

Pay securely here:
${PAY_LINK}

If you are experiencing difficulties with payment, please reach out — we may be able to help.

${FIRM_NAME} | ${FIRM_EMAIL}`
  },
  day14: {
    subject: `Third notice: Invoice ${invoice.invoice_number} — 14 days past due`,
    body: `Hi ${invoice.client_name},

Invoice ${invoice.invoice_number} for $${Number(invoice.balance).toFixed(2)} is now 14 days past due.

Pay here:
${PAY_LINK}

If there is a dispute or you have not received this invoice previously, contact us immediately at ${FIRM_EMAIL}.

${FIRM_NAME}`
  },
  day30: {
    subject: `Final notice: Invoice ${invoice.invoice_number} — 30 days past due`,
    body: `Hi ${invoice.client_name},

